Tezaura is a neo-gothic rock band from Brno, Czech Republic. The band is characterized by clean female vocal of the charismatic lead vocalist Lori, large participation of keyboards and synths and simple dreamy melodies accompanied by unconventional show.
 
The band was formed in summer 2010 and made it's first release EP "Daydreaming" in spring 2011. Soon the first music video "Mechanical Ballerina" came out as the prequel to a new album "Unleash the Butterflies", which finally saw the light of the world in September 2013.
 
During October and November 2013, the group presented the new album on "Unleash the Butterflies tour", which took place not only in Czechia but also in Austria, Poland, Slovakia and Hungary.  Nowadays the band actively performs and prepare new material for the next album.
